{"tid":2118284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[同我入黎聯署｜英國戰線］重啟BNO申請，篤藍屍灰","createTime":"2020-07-21T11:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T18:42:39.000Z","uid":44388,"like":46,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7c3824e23f61c3d6b4565825495d2e318cb068","tid":2118284,"uid":44388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:11:22.000Z","msg":"唔少父母有BNO既仔女，因為過左18歲<br />\n而唔會拎到dependant visa,<span class=\"blue\"> 果堆人點算？</span><br />\n<br />\n唔少手足響97年前，父母冇同佢地申請BNO<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">果堆人點算？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\"><strong>唯有重啟BNO申請，先可以幫到呢D手足</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">聯署link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/wmXiSJtAGUfP5J6n8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FwmXiSJtAGUfP5J6n8&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=3152eca6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/wmXiSJtAGUfP5J6n8</a></span><br />\n<br />\n同時，我地要不停篤灰<br />\n絕對唔可以俾理藍屍仆街黎到英國<br />\n將搜集到既資料，send 俾英國既passport office:<br />\nQueries@hmpo.gov.uk<br />\n<br />\n齊齊幫班撚樣做大灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b38ce1a70c3a1a48bdf04a1bc2c79965d6fc6f3","tid":2118284,"uid":44388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053e1544b4b485d5aa6dc801beb4625677265ee1","tid":2118284,"uid":44388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c8ead10dcef01cbbc194760f91b37e8dbff403","tid":2118284,"uid":44388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2145efd87d0ccbc6c2874f43253919e05e5e0e24","tid":2118284,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0