><br />\n<br />\n唔少手足響97年前，父母冇同佢地申請BNO<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">果堆人點算？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\"><strong>唯有重啟BNO申請，先可以幫到呢D手足</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">聯署link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/wmXiSJtAGUfP5J6n8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FwmXiSJtAGUfP5J6n8&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=3152eca6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/wmXiSJtAGUfP5J6n8</a></span><br />\n<br />\n同時，我地要不停篤灰<br />\n絕對唔可以俾理藍屍仆街黎到英國<br />\n將搜集到既資料，send 俾英國既passport office:<br />\nQueries@hmpo.gov.uk<br />\n<br />\n齊齊幫班撚樣做大灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"唔止英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其它國家都可以<br />\n另外去旅行見到黑警黑懲都可以試下提醒人哋入境處佢地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國間碟MI5: <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/report-suspicious-activity-to-mi5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Freport-suspicious-activity-to-mi5&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=fad8adab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/report-suspicious-activity-to-mi5</a><br />\n英國移民局:<a href=\"https://www.amsallegations.homeoffice.gov.uk/default.aspx/RenderForm/?F.Name=Lf62UB7cz4C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amsallegations.homeoffice.gov.uk%2Fdefault.aspx%2FRenderForm%2F%3FF.Name%3DLf62UB7cz4C&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=ad990a4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amsallegations.homeoffice.gov.uk/default.aspx/RenderForm/?F.Name=Lf62UB7cz4C</a><br />\n<br />\n美國間碟FBI: <a href=\"https://www.fbi.gov/tips\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fbi.gov%2Ftips&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=8d042963\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fbi.gov/tips</a><br />\n美國移民局: <a href=\"https://www.uscis.gov/report-fraud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscis.gov%2Freport-fraud&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=abc895f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uscis.gov/report-fraud</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲間碟ASIS: <a href=\"https://www.asio.gov.au/counter-espionage.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asio.gov.au%2Fcounter-espionage.html&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=eb4b6f1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.asio.gov.au/counter-espionage.html</a><br />\n澳洲移民局: <a href=\"https://www.homeaffairs.gov.au/help-and-support/departmental-forms/online-forms/border-watch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.homeaffairs.gov.au%2Fhelp-and-support%2Fdepartmental-forms%2Fonline-forms%2Fborder-watch&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=61464e84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.homeaffairs.gov.au/help-and-support/departmental-forms/online-forms/border-watch</a><br />\n<br />\n加拿大間碟CSIS:  <a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/security-intelligence-service/corporate/reporting-national-security-information.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fsecurity-intelligence-service%2Fcorporate%2Freporting-national-security-information.html&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=a6ed4e5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.canada.ca/en/security-intelligence-service/corporate/reporting-national-security-information.html</a><br />\n加拿大移民局: <a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/protect-fraud/report-fraud.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fimmigration-refugees-citizenship%2Fservices%2Fprotect-fraud%2Freport-fraud.html&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=50753020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees